Combine French onion dip mix, powdered buttermilk and chives. Set aside. In 2-gallon zipper-type storage bag, combine KELLOGG'S(R) CRISPIX(R) cereal and pretzels. Pour oil over cereal mixture. Close bag and gently toss cereal mixture until well coated. Add French onion dip mixture and close bag. Gently toss cereal mixture until well coated. Store in airtight container.